Package iiv.util

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ShowStatus
    ShowStatus defines methods for displaying status messages.
    UndoButtons
    Interface to allow notification of change in undo/redo status for updating button status.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BrowserControl
    A simple, static class to display a URL in the system browser.
    DisplayNumberFormat
    DisplayNumberFrom extends DecimalFormat to incorporate exponents and handles number format defaults for most iiV display components.
    DoCommand
    DoCommand holds a single undo or redo command.
    FileListElement
    FileListElement stores file name and class pairs for use as an element in a list.
    FormatTools
    Class to format numbers with exponentials.
    RunnableWithReturnObject
    This abstract class adds a variable to the runnable class for returning objects.
    UndoRedo
    UndoRedo is a class to track and perform undo/redo tasks.
